    <abstract>
      <t>   This document contains a specification of the the MPLS base YANG
   model.  The MPLS base YANG model serves as a base framework for
   configuring and managing an MPLS switching subsystem on an MPLS-
   enabled router.  It is expected that other MPLS YANG models (e.g.
   MPLS LSP Static, LDP or RSVP-TE YANG models) will augment the MPLS
   base YANG model.

